              <div id="collapse3" class="collapse">
                <div class="card-body">
                  Basant is the Annual Alumni Reunion of Indian Institute of Technology (Indian School of Mines), Dhanbad. It is a fest which unites all the members of IIT ISM, either he is a student or he is an alumni. It is a event to recall that every 
